{"title":"API 指导说明","slug":"api-guide","date":"2017-03-26T03:30:00.000Z","updated":"2017-03-02T06:23:23.000Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/api-guide.json","excerpt":"","content":"<p>3.2/1450.</p>\n<h2 id=\"Document\"><a href=\"#Document\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Document\"></a>Document</h2><p><a href=\"https://github.com/yscoder/hexo-generator-restful/blob/master/README.md\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external\">https://github.com/yscoder/hexo-generator-restful/blob/master/README.md</a></p>\n<h3 id=\"Get-Hexo-Config\"><a href=\"#Get-Hexo-Config\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Get Hexo Config\"></a>Get Hexo Config</h3><p>获取所有 Hexo 配置（站点配置和主题配置）。</p>\n<h6 id=\"Request\"><a href=\"#Request\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Request\"></a>Request</h6><figure class=\"highlight plain\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><div class=\"line\">1</div></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><div class=\"line\">GET /api/site.json</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<h6 id=\"Response\"><a href=\"#Response\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Response\"></a>Response</h6><p>&lt;%= url_for(path) %&gt;<br><blockquote><p>Do not just seek happiness for yourself. Seek happiness for all. Through kindness. Through mercy.</p>\n<footer><strong>David Levithan</strong><cite>Wide Awake</cite></footer></blockquote></p>\n<p><a href=\"/antcloud-hexostatic/api/site.json\">/api/site.json</a></p>\n<h3 id=\"Get-Posts\"><a href=\"#Get-Posts\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Get Posts\"></a>Get Posts</h3><p>如果配置 <code>posts_size: 0</code> 则不分页，以下请求会获取全部文章。</p>\n<h6 id=\"Request-1\"><a href=\"#Request-1\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Request\"></a>Request</h6><figure class=\"highlight plain\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><div class=\"line\">1</div></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><div class=\"line\">GET /api/posts.json</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<h6 id=\"Response-1\"><a href=\"#Response-1\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Response\"></a>Response</h6><p>示例为分页配置下的数据，会包含分页属性 <code>total</code>、<code>pageSize</code>、<code>pageCount</code>，不分页的数据不包含这三项。</p>\n<p><a href=\"/antcloud-hexostatic/api/posts.json\">/api/posts.json</a></p>\n<h3 id=\"Get-Posts-By-Page\"><a href=\"#Get-Posts-By-Page\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Get Posts By Page\"></a>Get Posts By Page</h3><p>获取分页数据</p>\n<h6 id=\"Request-2\"><a href=\"#Request-2\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Request\"></a>Request</h6><figure class=\"highlight plain\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><div class=\"line\">1</div></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><div class=\"line\">GET /api/posts/:PageNum.json</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<h6 id=\"Response-2\"><a href=\"#Response-2\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Response\"></a>Response</h6><p><a href=\"/antcloud-hexostatic/api/posts/1.json\">/api/posts/1.json</a></p>\n<h3 id=\"Get-All-Tags\"><a href=\"#Get-All-Tags\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Get All Tags\"></a>Get All Tags</h3><p>获取所有文章标签，如果文章无标签则不生成。</p>\n<h6 id=\"Request-3\"><a href=\"#Request-3\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Request\"></a>Request</h6><figure class=\"highlight plain\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><div class=\"line\">1</div></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><div class=\"line\">GET /api/tags.json</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<h6 id=\"Response-3\"><a href=\"#Response-3\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Response\"></a>Response</h6><p><a href=\"/antcloud-hexostatic/api/tags.json\">/api/tags.json</a></p>\n<h3 id=\"Get-Posts-By-Tag\"><a href=\"#Get-Posts-By-Tag\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Get Posts By Tag\"></a>Get Posts By Tag</h3><p>获取某一标签下的所有文章</p>\n<h6 id=\"Request-4\"><a href=\"#Request-4\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Request\"></a>Request</h6><figure class=\"highlight plain\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><div class=\"line\">1</div></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><div class=\"line\">GET /api/tags/:TagName.json</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<h6 id=\"Response-4\"><a href=\"#Response-4\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Response\"></a>Response</h6><p><a href=\"/antcloud-hexostatic/api/tags/mpaas.json\">/api/tags/Hexo.json</a></p>\n<h3 id=\"Get-All-Categories\"><a href=\"#Get-All-Categories\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Get All Categories\"></a>Get All Categories</h3><p>获取所有文章分类，如果文章无分类则不生成。</p>\n<h6 id=\"Request-5\"><a href=\"#Request-5\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Request\"></a>Request</h6><figure class=\"highlight plain\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><div class=\"line\">1</div></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><div class=\"line\">GET /api/categories.json</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<h6 id=\"Response-5\"><a href=\"#Response-5\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Response\"></a>Response</h6><p>数据格式同 Get All Tags</p>\n<h3 id=\"Get-Posts-By-Categorie\"><a href=\"#Get-Posts-By-Categorie\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Get Posts By Categorie\"></a>Get Posts By Categorie</h3><p>获取某一分类下的所有文章</p>\n<h6 id=\"Request-6\"><a href=\"#Request-6\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Request\"></a>Request</h6><figure class=\"highlight plain\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><div class=\"line\">1</div></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><div class=\"line\">GET /api/categories/:CategorieName.json</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<h6 id=\"Response-6\"><a href=\"#Response-6\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Response\"></a>Response</h6><p>数据格式同 Get Posts By Tag</p>\n<h3 id=\"Get-Post-By-Slug\"><a href=\"#Get-Post-By-Slug\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Get Post By Slug\"></a>Get Post By Slug</h3><p>根据文章别名获取文章详细信息</p>\n<h6 id=\"Request-7\"><a href=\"#Request-7\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Request\"></a>Request</h6><figure class=\"highlight plain\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><div class=\"line\">1</div></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><div class=\"line\">GET /api/articles/:Slug.json</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<h6 id=\"Response-7\"><a href=\"#Response-7\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Response\"></a>Response</h6><p><a href=\"/antcloud-hexostatic/api/articles/test2.json\">ç/api/articles/test2.json</a></p>\n","categories":[{"name":"lab","path":"api/categories/lab.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"hello world","path":"api/tags/hello world.json"}]}